 may instead put them all at risk"--cProvided by publisher. 0aWomen spiesvFiction. 0aHusbandsxDeathvFiction. 0aNazisvFiction. 0aInterpersonal relationsvFiction. 0aRevengevFiction. 0aWorld War, 1939-1945xUnderground movementsvFiction. 0aRiviera (France)vFiction. 0aLarge type books. 7aHistorical fiction.2lcgft  c(OCoLC)1225190306  c4732d4732